---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import FeatureCard from '../components/FeatureCard.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About isHistory"
  description="isHistory is a curated digital archive dedicated to preserving the human stories behind our technological landscape — from the earliest computing machines to the AI systems of today."
  pageType="about"
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- Section 1: Hero / Origin Story                                 -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 via-white to-purple-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-950 dark:to-indigo-950 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <!-- Decorative blur orbs -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 dark:opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-indigo-300 dark:bg-indigo-600 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-purple-300 dark:bg-purple-600 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 dark:from-indigo-400 dark:to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Mapping the Digital Past
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        isHistory is a curated digital archive dedicated to preserving the human stories behind our technological landscape — from the earliest computing machines to the AI systems of today.
      </p>
      <!-- Pull-quote callout -->
      <div class="mt-10 mx-auto max-w-xl">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-indigo-200 dark:border-indigo-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm px-8 py-6">
          <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-snug">
            No code. Just the decisions, debates, and forgotten moments that built the digital world.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- Section 2: Mission – Why This Archive Exists                    -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
          Why This Archive Exists
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Technology moves fast. Innovations that once seemed revolutionary are quickly forgotten — not just the machines, but the people who built them, the arguments that shaped them, and the failures that paved the way for success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Card: The Problem -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-rose-100 dark:border-rose-800/50 bg-rose-50 dark:bg-rose-950/50 p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-rose-100 text-rose-600 dark:bg-rose-900 dark:text-rose-400">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">The Forgetting</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Technology erases its own history. The faster it moves, the more it discards — not just outdated tools, but the reasoning behind them, the debates that defined them, and the people whose work made them possible. isHistory was founded to halt that erosion: to trace, index, and safeguard the narrative blueprints of computing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: The Thesis -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-800/50 bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-950/50 p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 dark:bg-indigo-900 dark:text-indigo-400">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Understanding Lineage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            We believe that understanding how technology came to be — the late-night breakthroughs, the career-ending mistakes, the cultural panics — is essential to knowing where it is going. Every framework, every algorithm, every paradigm shift has a lineage of human choices. isHistory documents those chains, one story at a time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card: The Positioning -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-950/50 p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 dark:bg-emerald-900 dark:text-emerald-400">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">An Archive of Narratives</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            This is not a news site. It is not a tutorial repository. It is an archive of narratives — deeply researched, immersive, and written for a general audience. Each series is built to be as durable as the stories it tells, offering readers an authoritative account they can return to years from now.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- Section 3: Archival Principles – How We Build                  -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-indigo-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-indigo-950/50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
          Archival Principles
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Every decision about content, structure, and technology is guided by these four principles.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <FeatureCard
          color="indigo"
          icon='<svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>'
          title="Depth Over Speed"
          description="Each article is long-form narrative history. We do not chase recency — we chase understanding. A chapter about the Dartmouth Conference takes as long as it needs to take, because getting the story right matters more than being first."
        />
        <FeatureCard
          color="emerald"
          icon='<svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>'
          title="Primary Sources First"
          description="Every claim is traced back to its source — original papers, letters, interviews, contemporaneous accounts. We do not rely on secondary summaries or Wikipedia chains. When a source is ambiguous, we say so. When a story has competing narratives, we present all of them."
        />
        <FeatureCard
          color="purple"
          icon='<svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" /></svg>'
          title="Layered, Not Linear"
          description="Content is organized into self-contained series, each covering a major technology domain. Within each series, multiple tracks run in parallel — overviews, profiles, and events — creating a layered reading experience. Follow one track linearly or cross-reference between them."
        />
        <FeatureCard
          color="amber"
          icon='<svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>'
          title="Open & Accessible"
          description="All content is published without paywalls, sign-ups, or tracking. The archive is built with web standards, self-hosted fonts for privacy, and structured data so that both humans and AI agents can discover and use it."
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- Section 4: Archivist – Ishaan                                   -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
          The Archivist
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50/50 via-white to-purple-50/50 dark:from-indigo-950/30 dark:via-gray-900 dark:to-purple-950/30 p-8 sm:p-10 shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-8">
            <!-- Avatar / Monogram -->
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <div class="inline-flex h-20 w-20 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 dark:from-indigo-500 dark:to-purple-500 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/25">
                <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">I</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Bio -->
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">Ishaan</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-4">Creator & Curator</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
                After years building web applications and realizing he could name every JavaScript framework but not a single person behind the ARPANET, Ishaan launched isHistory to fill that gap. With a background in web development and a deep fascination for the human history of technology, he ensures that the engineering stories behind the tools we use every day are not lost to time.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                He researches, writes, and edits every chapter — aiming to make complex technical history accessible to a general audience without sacrificing accuracy or depth.
              </p>
              <!-- Links -->
              <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
                <a
                  href="https://github.com/chatbot-x"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:text-indigo-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-400 hover:border-indigo-300 dark:hover:border-indigo-700"
                >
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
                  GitHub
                </a>
                <a
                  href="mailto:hello@ishistory.dev"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:text-indigo-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-400 hover:border-indigo-300 dark:hover:border-indigo-700"
                >
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
                  Write
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- Section 5: Infrastructure                                       -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-gray-900 dark:bg-black">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">
          Built to Last
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The archive is engineered for performance, privacy, and longevity. Every technical decision is made with the understanding that this content must remain accessible for decades.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Astro -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 bg-gray-800/50 p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-indigo-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Astro</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Static-first framework, zero client JS by default. Built for content-driven sites that need to load instantly and last indefinitely.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Cloudflare Pages -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 bg-gray-800/50 p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-orange-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-400">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Cloudflare Pages</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Edge deployment on a global CDN. Pages are served from the nearest data center to every reader, worldwide.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- TailwindCSS -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 bg-gray-800/50 p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-400">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">TailwindCSS 4</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Utility-first styling with full light and dark mode support. CSS-first configuration — no JavaScript config needed.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pagefind -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 bg-gray-800/50 p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Pagefind</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Static search index that works offline. No server, no tracking, no external dependencies — search that respects privacy.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- JSON-LD + llms.txt -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 bg-gray-800/50 p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-emerald-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">JSON-LD + llms.txt</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Structured data for search engines and AI agents. Every page is machine-readable, ensuring discoverability for both humans and the tools they use.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Collections -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-700/50 bg-gray-800/50 p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-amber-500/50 hover:bg-gray-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Content Collections</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Zod-validated frontmatter with TypeScript autocompletion. Type-safe content means fewer errors and a more reliable archive.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- Section 6: CTA – Enter the Archive                              -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-indigo-700 dark:from-indigo-800 dark:via-purple-900 dark:to-indigo-950 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <!-- Decorative blur orbs -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute top-10 left-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-white blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-20 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-purple-300 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight mb-4">
        Enter the Archive
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-indigo-100 leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Dive into the archive and discover the human stories behind the technology that shapes our world.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <!-- Primary CTA -->
        <a
          href="/series/minds-and-machines/"
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-white px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-indigo-700 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-900/30 transition-all hover:bg-indigo-50 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        >
          Start with Minds &amp; Machines
          <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <!-- Secondary CTA -->
        <a
          href="/series/"
